narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I developed a higher understanding of grammatical structures and applications of the Russian language. I also learned about 19th century Russian history.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The lessons on Russian history were very helpful in expanding my knowledge of Russian society and culture. The course can be improved by offering it not online but in Saint Petersburg as was originally planned before the pandemic.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would only recommend this course to students who are serious in their Russian language studies. If they are interested in the field, this is a great course for them.
